@startuml
title Sequence: Staff marks attendance
actor Staff
participant "Browser / UI" as UI
participant "Attendance View" as View
participant "Subject Service" as SubjectSvc
database "Attendance DB" as DB

Staff -> UI: Open Attendance Module
UI -> View: Request student list (subject, date)
View -> SubjectSvc: Fetch subject & session
SubjectSvc --> View: Student list
View --> UI: Render list
Staff -> UI: Mark present/absent
UI -> View: Submit attendance
View -> DB: Save attendance records
DB --> View: Confirm saved
View --> UI: Show confirmation
@enduml
